Subject: Re: [T2] Windshield Wiper Questions

Take the motor out, take the arm pivots apart (where they go through the body) and clean and grease everything. Also clean the commutator on the motor.  

Don't run your wipers anymore than you have to until then. You will burn up the motor... 

Chris
